summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 64W page 155 of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Lots 1-4 incl., Block 15, Lots 8-12, incl., Block 15, and Lots 9-12 incl., Block 16, all in McCallister's Addition, located in area west of 2nd Ave. So. from alley north of Bennett St. to Brandon St., from Duplex Residence High Density (RD 5000) Zone to General Industrial (IG) Zone.
